INSERT INTO packs (
                package_id,
                pack_type,
                language,
                name,
                description,
                status,
                legacy_version,
                legacy_file_path,
                legacy_sha256
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, 'draft', 'legacy-placeholder', NULL, NULL)
            ON CONFLICT (package_id) DO UPDATE SET
                name = EXCLUDED.name,
                description = EXCLUDED.description
